{"tid":1047282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧：美國及中國即將達成貿易協議","createTime":"2019-03-05T00:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T02:22:21.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"08a6ecdda7bdb1bbb5da350cff98858a36747d02","tid":1047282,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:27:45.000Z","msg":"05/03/2019 08:10<br />\n<br />\n　　《經濟通通訊社５日專訊》美國國務卿蓬佩奧表示，認為美中兩國即將達成貿易協議，希望令貿易變得公平互惠，並將所有關稅及貿易壁壘消除。　　他補充，未來數周美中兩國有望達成協議，並消除中國對大豆等主要農產品的報復性關稅。　　較早時白宮經濟顧問委員會主席哈西特接受訪問時指，美國貿易代表萊特希澤與中國的談判取得很大進展，雙方有可能達成協議。　　熟悉談判情況的消息人士表示，美中兩國在確保中國履行承諾的機制上仍有大量工作要做，如果不能在執行機制上談攏，談判仍有可能破裂。（ｍｎ）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=macro&amp;newsid=ETN290305231\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Dmacro%26newsid%3DETN290305231&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=6ba35107\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=macro&amp;newsid=ETN290305231</a>"},{"pid":"127ed05c1ea5a5d570026fb02b6177863730c240","tid":1047282,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要破裂"},{"pid":"afd20be386c13cedea1e7b64c4195c19233eff70","tid":1047282,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"127ed05c1ea5a5d570026fb02b6177863730c240","tid":1047282,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要破裂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:53:39.000Z","msg":"無可能啦，侵侵要政績爭取連任<br />\n習大大唔使任何政績都可以連任<br />\n所以侵侵急住同中國簽協議就真"},{"pid":"24d72089eb4b046cd92c740df41a8a234dd5303a","tid":1047282,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:55:31.000Z","msg":"德專家預測北